This is the new 'official' home of the 787-8 for Flightgear.

After gitorious closed down and former maintainer Omega95 retired, islandmonkey created this Github repo. We'll try to gather open merge requests and improvements from the old gitorious repo here.

Install
-------
Rename Aircraft folder to '787-8'

WIKI ARTICLE : http://wiki.flightgear.org/Boeing_787-8_Dreamliner
